{"tid":58261,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實美股交易有無交收費?","createTime":"2016-12-28T16:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T04:37:18.000Z","uid":65324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a52bcc62fc0a5ce2786df8da6520ad71b66d99","tid":58261,"uid":65324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"之前係富途開左個戶口，見美股好似好玩過港股，想買下美股，前排再係8 Securities開左個戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我發現富途買美股有收交收費$0.003/股，最低USD$3/筆，點解既？ 我見8 Securities、耀才、新鴻基金融果啲都無收既...例如8仔證券剩係得證監徵費同交易徵費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為美股係一股一股咁買，咁如果我用300蚊美金係富途買美股，咪差唔多收左1%手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無專業既巴絲們可以解答一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFutu: <a href=\"https://www.futu5.com/faq/topic43\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.futu5.com%2Ffaq%2Ftopic43&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c7e1995a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.futu5.com/faq/topic43</a><br />\n8 Securities: <a href=\"https://www.8securities.com/tc-trading/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8securities.com%2Ftc-trading%2F&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b5010fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.8securities.com/tc-trading/</a><br />\n耀才: <a href=\"http://www.bsgroup.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bsgroup.com.hk%2F&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=60e3fee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bsgroup.com.hk/</a><br />\nSHK Direct: <a href=\"http://download.shkf.com/fees/pricing-table-os-tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdownload.shkf.com%2Ffees%2Fpricing-table-os-tc.pdf&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2w